\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The University of South Africa \'28UNISA\'29 is a public higher education institution whose programmes have been accredited by the CHE. \line \line The Institution is currently applying for the accreditation of a Diploma in Civil Engineering programme which will be offered in the distance mode of delivery from the Muckleneuk\'2C Pretoria\'2C Main Campus. \line \line The Institution has also applied for the accreditation of the following programmes which have been accredited\'3A\line - Advanced Certificate in Engineering Technology in Civil Engineering \line - Advanced Diploma in Mining Engineering\cell \pard 

\intbl \row \pard 
\line \par\pard\trowd\trqc \trpaddl113\trpaddt113\trpaddb113\trpaddr113\trpaddfl3\trpaddft3\trpaddfb3\trpaddfr3\trgaph100\trrh100\trleft36
